NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::PERLANCAR::MetaResources - Set meta resources for
    dists

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.043 of
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::PERLANCAR::MetaResources (from Perl distribution
    Dist-Zilla-Plugin-PERLANCAR-MetaResources), released on 2021-05-07.

SYNOPSIS
    In dist.ini:

     [PERLANCAR::MetaResources]

DESCRIPTION
    Code is based on Dist::Zilla::Plugin::MetaResourcesFromGit. The
    difference is the defaults: in this plugin, homepage by default is set
    to MetaCPAN release page instead of github wiki.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Dist-Zilla-Plugin-PERLANCAR-MetaResources>
    .

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-Dist-Zilla-Plugin-PERLANCAR-MetaResou
    rces>.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests on the bugtracker website
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-Dist-Zilla-Plugin-PERLANCAR-MetaResou
    rces/issues>

    When submitting a bug or request, please include a test-file or a patch
    to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or desired feature.

